videos.description: Anton Beard comes right out of a spin move and drains the 3-pointer for Arkansas.
videos.headline: Beard dribbles in circles and drains three

videos.description: C.J. Jones hits nothing but net for the Razorbacks on the fast break.
videos.headline: Jones hits the transition 3

videos.description: Arkansas's Daniel Gafford rocks the pick-and-roll to perfection and punishes the rim with one-hand.
videos.headline: Gafford throws down with ferocity

videos.description: Amir Coffey takes the contact and still gets the bucket for the Golden Gophers.
videos.headline: Coffey finishes frenetic layup through foul

videos.description: Amir Coffey makes a nice cut and sends it in with two hands.
videos.headline: Coffey cuts on the baseline and throws it down

videos.description: C.J. Jones is unconscious with all 15 of his points coming from behind the arc for Arkansas.
videos.headline: Jones hits his fifth triple

videos.description: Arkansas' Daniel Gafford gets up for two big blocks on the same possession.
videos.headline: Gafford sends it back twice

videos.description: Arkansas head coach Mike Anderson sits down with Matt Schick and Pat Bradley to discuss his team's win over No. 14 Minnesota.
videos.headline: Anderson says bench and seniors were key to upset

videos.description: Jordan Murphy shines with 20 points and 10 rebounds, but it wasn't enough for the Golden Gophers as they fall to the Razorbacks 95-79.
videos.headline: Arkansas takes over to defeat No. 14 Minnesota
